            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 text-center well"  style="margin-bottom:25px;">
            <div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9">
                <iframe class="embed-responsive-item" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/R0JKCYZ8hng?rel=0&modestbranding=1&autohide=1&showinfo=0&controls=0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
            <p>"It's easy to play any musical instrument: all you have to do is touch the right key at the right time and the instrument will play itself."</p>
            <footer class="pull-right"><em>- Johann Sebastian Bach</em></footer>
        </div>
    </div>
